#   | Copy it to a file names ".env" and fill in the values before running the application.  |
#   | The ".env" FILE SHOULD NOT BE COMMITTED TO VERSION CONTROL.                            |
#   | WITHOUT A PROPER .env FILE, THE APPLICATION WILL NOT RUN.                              |
